Internationalization foundation

The web App Router is locale-prefixed with `next-intl`. Public and admin routes live under `app/[locale]` with MVP locales `en` and `ar`, default locale `en`, and an always-on locale prefix. The root locale layout sets `<html lang>` and `<html dir>` from the active locale so Arabic renders `rtl` even before full string translation. Locale message files live in `apps/web/messages/`; string translation is handled by the follow-up i18n tickets, not by the foundation layer.

